Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
this is a good thing for the reason that it promotes a sense of community among yhe students by forcing them to live in housing units together. it also serves to foster friendships that might not have ever budded otherwise. on campus housing may be bad however, because it is extra money a student has to pay which is ridiculous if their family lives within a reasonable vicinity to the campus